description:
Are you freaking out about sending your kids back to school?
 
If you are worried or scared, today I'm teaching you what you can do to stop spiraling out of control with worry and fear.
 
Why am I doing this? Because I know if you don't get control of your mind then you'll lose control of your mouth!
